article.description: — Ville Tahvanainen had 19 points and Bradley romped past Jackson State 83-60 on Thursday night.
article.headline: Tahvanainen leads Bradley past Jackson St. 83-60
article.linkText: Tahvanainen leads Bradley past Jackson St. 83-60
article.story: PEORIA, Ill. -- — Ville Tahvanainen had 19 points and Bradley romped past Jackson State 83-60 on Thursday night. Ja’Shon Henry and Terry Nolan Jr. added 16 points each for the Braves (5-2). Elijah Childs had 10 points and seven rebounds. Tristan Jarrett had 22 points for the Tigers (0-4). Jayveous McKinnis scored a career-high 21 points and had nine rebounds. ------ For more AP college basketball coverage: https://apnews.com/Collegebasketball and http://twitter.com/AP--Top25 ------ This was generated by Automated Insights, http://www.automatedinsights.com/ap, using data from STATS LLC, https://www.stats.com
